{"tid":2168224,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"草娥新東家代表被起底！　7年前曾公開「嚴厲訓斥雪炫」…","createTime":"2020-08-21T15:04:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-21T19:21:08.000Z","uid":74065,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"2d46558a54d1c78050ece2749b9d92c182f95190","tid":2168224,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T15:04:57.000Z","msg":"南韓女團AOA前成員草娥在2017年退出團體，銷聲匿跡了3年，近日終於回歸，並且確定簽入前東家FNC創社元老金英善成立的公司，成為該公司首位簽約藝人。而隨著草娥簽進新東家的消息傳出，韓網論壇也出現了起底公司老闆的文章，驚見金英善竟曾出現在FNC娛樂6年前的實境節目中，並且讓許多觀眾留下了強烈的印象。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2617/d2617710.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2617%2Fd2617710.jpg&h=c6207087&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n▲草娥簽約新東家，正式回歸演藝圈。（圖／CFP）<br />\n<br />\n據悉，草娥攜手新的經紀公司「Great M娛樂」，重啟演藝之路，老闆正是前東家FNC創社元老金英善，而對方在FNC娛樂不但是開國元老，還擔任了常務的職位，此次出走創立新公司，兩人也延續以前結下的因緣簽約。草娥復出的消息傳出後，有南韓網友在得知公司老闆的名字後，翻出了2013年開播的《清潭洞111》片段，驚見金英善當時登場的模樣。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5088/d5088516.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5088%2Fd5088516.jpg&h=8dda94cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲雪炫與金英善在節目中的片段。（圖／翻攝《清潭洞111》片段）<br />\n<br />\n影片中可看到金英善當時是FNC娛樂的理事，在練習室中登場後，當著許多後輩練習生以及成員面前對雪炫說道：「雪炫妳好像胖了？體重多少？」讓雪炫非常害怕，吞吞吐吐、沒辦法好好回答，接著她放大音量追問「超過50嗎？」，還嚴肅地指責表示：「聽說本部長要妳減肥，妳還說減肥會生病，不能減？」<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5088/d5088517.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5088%2Fd5088517.jpg&h=41709451&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲雪炫曾因超過50公斤被金英善訓斥。（圖／翻攝《清潭洞111》片段）<br />\n<br />\n雪炫小聲回答金英善「沒有說過（那樣的話）」，接著也認錯道歉，當時節目播出後，引起熱烈討論，成為了節目的著名片段，如今隨著金英善設立新公司、簽下草娥，再度成為話題，南韓網友看了片段紛紛表示「竟然是那位&hellip;」、「這女的講話好沒教養」、「看過節目的都知道她對所屬藝人講話都超打擊人自尊」，但也有人認為「怎樣都比韓成豪好」、「反正草娥是深思過才簽約的吧」。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pe7GTMA79-Y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dpe7GTMA79-Y&d=4FeJsexKtrFIFozdf5QThv8K46P7%2BXxs1F7ZCKkfkQw%3D&h=5a54d411\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pe7GTMA79-Y</a><br />\n▲雪炫被訓斥片段。（影片取自YouTube，如遭刪除請見諒。）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n抵啦死欺凌賓妹"},{"pid":"d1587b014216a96a971058e14ff6fb859352cac6","tid":2168224,"uid":235015,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T15:10:56.000Z","msg":"屌第一眼以為第一張圖個雪炫係代表<br />\n同宜家完全唔同樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71df59a2c333e26811e2548b4c52ef19ac1b98a1","tid":2168224,"uid":74065,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"d1587b014216a96a971058e14ff6fb859352cac6","tid":2168224,"uid":235015,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T15:10:56.000Z","msg":"屌第一眼以為第一張圖個雪炫係代表<br />\n同宜家完全唔同樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T15:11:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200708/357547203746729984.jpeg/2O8oqHyVtXedc11ukEyqbVzH2j2pJW6syZ_RTsmf0U4?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200708%2F357547203746729984.jpeg%2F2O8oqHyVtXedc11ukEyqbVzH2j2pJW6syZ_RTsmf0U4%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=aeb6805b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://jdailyhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/AOA%E9%9B%AA%E7%82%AB%E7%B4%A0%E9%A1%8F%E6%81%90%E6%80%96%E8%B6%95%E5%AE%A2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fjdailyhk.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F05%2FAOA%25E9%259B%25AA%25E7%2582%25AB%25E7%25B4%25A0%25E9%25A1%258F%25E6%2581%2590%25E6%2580%2596%25E8%25B6%2595%25E5%25AE%25A2.jpg&h=91367051&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e22be962d0590a85395e113da3f1ed9ab563cce3","tid":2168224,"uid":68678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T15:35:44.000Z","msg":"斯凌師<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f71d9eb89cb72600f07f0f6bc77fdf5ca23278